snippet: Rory McIlroy, currently ranked No. 1 in the world, shot an opening-round 64 Thursday to share the lead with three other golfers at the BMW Championship. Tiger Woods shot a 65, good for fifth place.
abstract: Rory McIlroy shoots an impressive opening-round 64 to share the lead with three other golfers at the BMW Championship; Tiger Woods, McIlroy's playing partner, is tied for fifth place.
lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy, currently ranked No. 1 in the world, shot an opening-round 64 Thursday to share the lead with three other golfers at the BMW Championship. Tiger Woods shot a 65, good for fifth place.

headline.seo: BMW Championship — Anything Woods Can Do, McIlroy Can Do Better
headline.main: Anything Woods Can Do, McIlroy Does Better
headline.print_headline: Anything Woods Can Do, McIlroy Does Better
